            "value": "语音激活"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Classic mode auto-scrolls at a fixed pace so you can rehearse without using the microphone.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "经典模式以固定速度自动滚屏，无需使用麦克风即可排练。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Voice-Activated mode advances only while the microphone hears speech, which helps you pause naturally.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "语音激活模式仅在麦克风检测到声音时才会滚动，帮助你自然停顿。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Word Tracking mode listens to your speech and keeps the highlighted word close to what you are actually saying.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "跟词模式会聆听你的发言，并将高亮词保持在你实际朗读位置附近。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
